{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/saat-nintendo-mengabaikan-sumpah-dan-akhirnya-merilis-night-trap/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Saat Nintendo Mengabaikan Sumpah dan Akhirnya Merilis “Night Trap”","content":"<p>Tahukah kamu kalau tahun ‘90an adalah era kelahiran genre <em>video game</em> “Gore and Violence” alias kesadisan &amp; kekerasan? Sesuatu yang sebelumnya tidak ada dan tidak terpikirkan akan lahir dari medium hiburan seperti <em>video game</em>.</p>\n<p><em>Game-game offensive</em> (setidaknya untuk ukuran pada masa itu) muncul di era ini, dimana hal itu mengubah drastis citra <em>video game</em> dari yang sebelumnya sebagai ‘hiburan anak-anak’ menjadi ‘sesuatu yang dapat membahayakan anak-anak’ dengan pengaruh kekerasan dan unsur seksualitas yang tidak baik.</p>\n<p>Dari banyak<em> game</em> yang mengambil rute <em>“violence and sex-related</em>”, dua judul muncul sebagai yang teratas menjadi perhatian kelompok-kelompok konservatif yang merasa<em> game-game</em> ini sebagai ancaman untuk anak-anak.</p>\n<p>Keduanya adalah “Mortal Kombat” dari Midway (Arcade) serta “Night Trap” dari Digital Pictures (Sega CD).</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46987\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46987\" data-attachment-id=\"46987\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/saat-nintendo-mengabaikan-sumpah-dan-akhirnya-merilis-night-trap/attachment/30-mortal-kombat/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/30-mortal-kombat.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Mortal Kombat (Arcade). Sumber gambar: RedBubble\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Mortal Kombat (Arcade). Sumber gambar: RedBubble&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/30-mortal-kombat-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/30-mortal-kombat.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46987\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/30-mortal-kombat.jpg\" alt=\"Mortal Kombat (Arcade). Sumber gambar: RedBubble\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/30-mortal-kombat.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/30-mortal-kombat-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46987\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Mortal Kombat (Arcade). (Sumber: RedBubble)</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46979\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46979\" data-attachment-id=\"46979\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/saat-nintendo-mengabaikan-sumpah-dan-akhirnya-merilis-night-trap/attachment/31-night-trap/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/31-night-trap.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Night Trap (Sega CD). Sumber gambar: i-Mockery\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Night Trap (Sega CD). Sumber gambar: i-Mockery&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/31-night-trap-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/31-night-trap.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46979\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/31-night-trap.jpg\" alt=\"Night Trap (Sega CD). Sumber gambar: i-Mockery\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/31-night-trap.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/31-night-trap-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46979\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Night Trap (Sega CD). (Sumber: i-Mockery)</p></div></p>\n<p>Untuk era sekarang kedua judul ini, jika dilihat dari konten dan penyajiannya, termasuk ‘biasa-biasa’ saja. Tidak terlalu gimana-gimana banget.</p>\n<p>Tapi di era ‘90an? Dua game ini menghebohkan karena keluar dari pakem standard sebuah video game; yang dulu (dan sampai sekarang, untuk beberapa kalangan) dianggap sebagai mainan anak-anak. Mortal Kombat penuh darah serta kekerasan yang dianggap berlebihan, dan Night Trap dengan muatan kekerasan pada wanita serta adanya unsur sensualitas (yang masih asing untuk <em>video game</em> masa itu).</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46986\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46986\" data-attachment-id=\"46986\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/saat-nintendo-mengabaikan-sumpah-dan-akhirnya-merilis-night-trap/attachment/28-mortal-kombat/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/28-mortal-kombat.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Kekerasan di Mortal Kombat. Sumber gambar: GQ\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Kekerasan di Mortal Kombat. Sumber gambar: GQ&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/28-mortal-kombat-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/28-mortal-kombat.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46986\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/28-mortal-kombat.jpg\" alt=\"Kekerasan di Mortal Kombat. Sumber gambar: GQ\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/28-mortal-kombat.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/28-mortal-kombat-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46986\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kekerasan di Mortal Kombat. (Sumber: GQ)</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46982\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46982\" data-attachment-id=\"46982\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/saat-nintendo-mengabaikan-sumpah-dan-akhirnya-merilis-night-trap/attachment/37-night-trap/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/37-night-trap.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sensualitas di Night Trap. Sumber gambar: GiantBomb\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sensualitas di Night Trap. Sumber gambar: GiantBomb&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/37-night-trap-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/37-night-trap.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46982\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/37-night-trap.jpg\" alt=\"Sensualitas di Night Trap. Sumber gambar: GiantBomb\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/37-night-trap.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/37-night-trap-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46982\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sensualitas di Night Trap. (Sumber: GiantBomb)</p></div></p>\n<p>Bahkan (sepertinya) karena kedua <em>game</em> inilah, <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/steam-dalam-ancaman-blokir-pemerintah-akankah-lord-gaben-bertindak/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">lahir badan rating ESRB</a> di Amerika Serikat, dan disusul negara-negara lain seperti Eropa dan bahkan Indonesia.</p>\n<p>Karena menimbulkan polemik di antara orang tua, Komite Senat Amerika Serikat memanggil pelaku industri <em>video game</em> saat itu untuk dimintai keterangan pada Desember 1993. Ini kira-kira seperti pemanggilan DPR pada warga negara Indonesia untuk satu kasus tertentu.</p>\n<p>Dua senator Amerika Serikat yang saat itu terkenal ‘super anti <em>video game</em>’, Sen. Joseph Lieberman &amp; Sen. Herbert Kohl, memimpin panel khusus bertujuan “memberangus <em>video game</em> (yang mengandung kekerasan dan seksualitas)”. Salah satu yang memberikan keterangan saat itu adalah Presiden Nintendo Amerika Serikat, Howard Lincoln.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46988\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46988\" data-attachment-id=\"46988\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/saat-nintendo-mengabaikan-sumpah-dan-akhirnya-merilis-night-trap/attachment/36-mortal-kombat/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/36-mortal-kombat.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"36-mortal-kombat\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Senator USA. (Sumber: RetroGameNetwork)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/36-mortal-kombat-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/36-mortal-kombat.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46988\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/36-mortal-kombat.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/36-mortal-kombat.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/36-mortal-kombat-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46988\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Senator USA. (Sumber: RetroGameNetwork)</p></div></p>\n<p>Howard Lincoln, dalam kapasitasnya sebagai Boss Nintendo di Amerika saat itu, mengatakan kalau <em>game</em> Night Trap tidak akan muncul di platform Nintendo. Sementara Mortal Kombat akan mengalami sensor ketat (penghilangan efek darah &amp; fatalities).</p>\n<p>“Dalam beberapa tahun belakangan ini, <em>game-game</em> bertema kekerasan mulai memasuki pasar, dan tentu saja yang saya maksud adalah Mortal Kombat serta <em>Night Trap</em>” ujar Lincoln di depan Komite Senat yang dipimpin oleh Lieberman &amp; Kohl.</p>\n<p>“Saya akan katakan ini, dan harap dicatat, kalau Night Trap tidak akan muncul di platform Nintendo. Game ini tidak lolos kriteria kami. Game ini… yang mempromosikan kekerasan pada wanita, benar-benar tidak punya tempat di masyarakat kita” sambung Boss Nintendo tersebut dengan tegas.</p>\n<p>Dokumentasi acara dengar pendapat US Senate dengan Nintendo of America tahun 1993:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.c-span.org/video/standalone/?52848-1/video-game-violence\" width=\"512\" height=\"330\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46989\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46989\" data-attachment-id=\"46989\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/saat-nintendo-mengabaikan-sumpah-dan-akhirnya-merilis-night-trap/attachment/27-lincoln/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/27-lincoln.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"27-lincoln\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Boss Nintendo of America 1993. (Sumber: YouTube)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/27-lincoln-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/27-lincoln.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46989\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/27-lincoln.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/27-lincoln.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/27-lincoln-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46989\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Boss Nintendo of America 1993. (Sumber: YouTube)</p></div></p>\n<p>“Night Trap” sendiri merupakan game dengan genre ‘FMV <em>Interactive Movie’</em>. Dirilis tahun 1992 di masa-masa popularitas format CD untuk <em>video game</em> dimulai. Pada dasarnya merupakan<em> game</em> bertema <em>live-action</em> video, puzzle dan QTE/<em>Quick Time Event</em> (jika disamakan dengan genre era masa kini), Night Trap memiliki unsur kekerasan serta sensualitas yang lumayan tinggi untuk ukuran masa itu. Hal ini menjadikan Night Trap sebagai bahan pembicaraan, mengingat game ‘FMV <em>Interactive Movie</em>’ sebelumnya seperti “Dragon’s Lair” (1983) atau “Space Ace” (1984) lebih kartun dan komedik.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46990\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46990\" data-attachment-id=\"46990\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/saat-nintendo-mengabaikan-sumpah-dan-akhirnya-merilis-night-trap/attachment/26-dragons-lair/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/26-dragons-lair.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"26-dragons-lair\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Game Interactive Movie era ‘80an. (Sumber: YouTube)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/26-dragons-lair-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/26-dragons-lair.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46990\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/26-dragons-lair.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/26-dragons-lair.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/26-dragons-lair-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46990\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Game Interactive Movie era ‘80an. (Sumber: YouTube)</p></div></p>\n<p>Night Trap pertama dirilis untuk console Sega CD. Mungkin karena faktor itu juga Howard Lincoln sampai bersumpah tidak akan merilis Night Trap untuk Nintendo? Selain Sega CD, Night Trap juga pernah dirilis untuk 32X, 3DO, Microsoft Windows, hingga di console modern <em>current gen</em> seperti PlayStation 4 dan Xbox One.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46980\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46980\" data-attachment-id=\"46980\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/saat-nintendo-mengabaikan-sumpah-dan-akhirnya-merilis-night-trap/attachment/32-night-trap/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/32-night-trap.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"32-night-trap\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Night Trap versi PlayStation 4. (Sumber: Gematsu)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/32-night-trap-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/32-night-trap.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46980\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/32-night-trap.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/32-night-trap.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/32-night-trap-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46980\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Night Trap versi PlayStation 4. (Sumber: Gematsu)</p></div></p>\n<p>Lebih dari dua dekade kemudian, kebijakan di Nintendo untuk judul ini mengalami perubahan. Melalui <em>publisher</em> ‘kecil-kecil cabe rawit’ <em>Limited Run Games &amp; Screaming Villains, “Night Trap: 25<sup>th</sup> Anniversary Edition</em>” segera menyambangi Nintendo Switch. Akan ada dua format: digital (yang bisa dibeli di Nintendo Switch <em>e-Shop</em>) dan fisik alias <em>cartridge</em> seperti <em>game</em> Switch lainnya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46981\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46981\" data-attachment-id=\"46981\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/saat-nintendo-mengabaikan-sumpah-dan-akhirnya-merilis-night-trap/attachment/33-night-trap/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/33-night-trap.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"33-night-trap\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Howard Lincoln mungkin akan murka saat melihat ini. (Sumber: NintendoEverything)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/33-night-trap-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/33-night-trap.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46981\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/33-night-trap.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/33-night-trap.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/33-night-trap-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46981\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Howard Lincoln mungkin akan murka saat melihat ini. (Sumber: NintendoEverything)</p></div></p>\n<p>Sumpah atau janji Howard Lincoln di depan Komite Senat Amerika Serikat memang tidak berupa hal berkekuatan hukum tetap. Jadi saat Night Trap akhirnya masuk juga ke platform Nintendo, itu bukan salah siapa-siapa. Dunia <em>gaming</em> sangat cepat berubah dan bersifat dinamis. Sesuatu yang mungkin tidak terbayangkan oleh seorang Howard Lincoln ataupun para Senator Amerika Serikat yang tidak mengerti soal industri <em>video game</em> secara mendalam.</p>\n<p>Apakah game Night Trap itu <em>game</em> bagus? Saya bilang sih ini<em> game</em> yang <em>segmented</em>. <em>Game</em> FMV (F<em>ull Motion Video) Interactive Movie</em> memang keren di masa itu. Saya punya <em>console game</em> 3DO, dan banyak <em>game</em> FMV <em>Interactive Movie</em> model begini di sana. Jika kamu mau merasakan nuansa <em>game</em> yang menimbulkan kehebohan di era ‘90an dan punya Nintendo Switch, silakan mencobanya sendiri nanti.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/CAoCOXBE0yY\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"c2a86664-7127-5b95-b32e-46c3504d793e"}}}